       There might be complex GPU requirements that the bsub -gpu option
       and [1mGPU_REQ [22mparameter syntax cannot cover, including compound GPU
       requirements (for different GPU requirements for jobs on differ‐
       ent hosts, or for different parts of a parallel job) and alter‐
       nate GPU requirements (if more than one set of GPU requirements
       might be acceptable for a job to run). For complex GPU require‐
       ments, use the bsub -R command option, or the [1mRES_REQ [22mparameter
